\/2022\/08\/22\/amir-self-talk\/","url_meta":{"origin":15454,"position":0},"title":"\u2018Amir on Salat: Do you talk to your Nafs in prayer?","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 22, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu al-Husayn reported: It was said to \u2018Amir ibn Abdul Qays, may Allah have mercy on him, \u201cDo you talk to yourself in prayer?\u201d \u2018Amir said, \u201cYes. I tell myself to stand in front of the Lord Almighty and to turn away from what is in front of Him.\u201d Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":13973,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/05\/05\/seek-refuge-four-things\/","url_meta":{"origin":15454,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Dua: The Prophet seeks refuge from four things","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 5, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, would seek refuge in Allah from four things: from knowledge that does not benefit, from a heart without reverence, from a supplication that is unanswered, and from an ego that is never satisfied. Source: Sunan al-Nasa\u0304'i\u0304 5442 Grade:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34891,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/12\/31\/sufyan-khushu-salat\/","url_meta":{"origin":15454,"position":2},"title":"Sufyan on Salat: Reverence is required for sound prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 31, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Bishr ibn al-Harith reported: Sufyan al-Thawri, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cWhoever does not have reverence has spoiled his prayer.\u201d Source: Qu\u0304t al-Qulu\u0304b 2\/161 \u0639\u0646 \u0628\u0634\u0631 \u0628\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0627\u0631\u062b \u0642\u0627\u0644 \u0642\u0627\u0644 \u0633\u0641\u064a\u0627\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u062b\u0648\u0631\u064a \u0631\u062d\u0645\u0647 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u0645\u0646 \u0644\u0645 \u064a\u062e\u0634\u0639 \u0641\u0633\u062f\u062a \u0635\u0644\u0627\u062a\u0647 2\/161 \u0642\u0648\u062a \u0627\u0644\u0642\u0644\u0648\u0628 \u0641\u064a \u0645\u0639\u0627\u0645\u0644\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u062d\u0628\u0648\u0628","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":38531,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/12\/21\/place-of-sajdah\/","url_meta":{"origin":15454,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Sujud: Looking at place of prostration in prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 21, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, entered the Ka\u2019bah and his eyesight was not diverted from his place of prostration until he exited from it. Source: al-Sunan al-Kubra\u0301 lil-Bayhaqi\u0304 9726 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u062a\u0652 \u062f\u064e\u062e\u064e\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0